headline: African Development Bank Launches New Eur 1 Billion 2.500 Percent 5-Year Social Benchmark [announcement]
summary: On Wednesday 21st May 2025, the African Development Bank AfDB rated Aaa/AAA/AAA by Moody's / S&P / Fitch, priced a EUR 1 billion 5-year Social Benchmark due May 2030 at Mid-Swaps +28bps, equivalent...
